Ms Weeks and her two sons are among the grieving family members who lost loved ones in the tragic and baffling disappearance of Malaysia Airlines flight MH370.

In a candid interview  airing this Tuesday on SBS Dateline, the mother tells of her families gruelling year without their devoted husband and father Paul Weeks.

